  "remarks": "\nBrigadier General Aung Aung, as Commander of the 33rd Light Infantry Division of the Myanmar Army is responsible for serious human rights violations committed against the Rohingya population in Rakhine state. These include unlawful killings and systematic burning of Rohingya houses and buildings.",
